column1: Baby Barnaby's////Went today and honestly i do not understand why everyone is crazy about this place.....so the prices are cheap....ok maybe a reason but there are way better places to eat at on the cheap......service was fast and good...hence the one star...the food....i had the green eggs....OMG....heart attack waiting to happen....one bite and i was done.....my bf had the eggwhite plate....abit ok....i know we will not be ging back....
